tion gepr\u00e4gt ist, und verf\u00fcgen \u00fcber eigene, erneuerte Statuten. Sie unterstehen der Jurisdiktion des Bischofs von Sitten. Die Klosterkirche von C., Anfang des 18. Jh. errichtet, wurde 1994 restauriert."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q24007899", "itemLabel": "ch\u00e2teau d'Arbignon (monast\u00e8re)", "dhsid": "011860", "namefr": "Monast\u00e8re de Collombey", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monast%C3%A8re_de_Collombey", "namede": "Bernhardinerinnenkloster Collombey", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bernhardinerinnenkloster_Collombey", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q811979", "instanceofLabel": "structure architecturale", "gndid": "7737407-1"}, {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q24007899", "itemLabel": "ch\u00e2teau d'Arbignon (monast\u00e8re)", "dhsid": "011860", "namefr": "Monast\u00e8re de Collombey", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monast%C3%A8re_de_Collombey", "namede": "Bernhardinerinnenkloster Collombey", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bernhardinerinnenkloster_Collombey", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q751876", "instanceofLabel": "ch\u00e2teau", "gndid": "7737407-1"}, {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q24007899", "itemLabel": "ch\u00e2teau d'Arbignon (monast\u00e8re)", "dhsid": "011860", "namefr": "Monast\u00e8re de Collombey", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monast%C3%A8re_de_Collombey", "namede": "Bernhardinerinnenkloster Collombey", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bernhardinerinnenkloster_Collombey", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q44613", "instanceofLabel": "monast\u00e8re", "gndid": "7737407-1"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q24007899", "wikipedia_page_title": "Bernhardinerinnenk